  dcterms:description "Market data sourced from: Mordor Intelligence (2025), Grand View Research (2023-2025), Market Data Forecast (2024-2026), Research & Markets (2024), European Commission BUILD UP initiative, International Sustainable Energy Conference (2025). Fire classification references: EN 13501-1, BS 8414, Approved Document B. Thermal standards: EN ISO 6946, EN ISO 10077, EN ISO 7345. Energy directives: EPBD 2024/1275, Directive 2024/1275/EU, Construction Products Regulation (CPR) 2024. Retrofit programs: Energiesprong, 4RinEU, INFINITE project, Life Giga Regio Factory, DigiFab (Horizon Europe)."@en .